Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:30.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:148961,150171}It doesn't look well…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:31.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150171,151005}Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:31.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151005,151839}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:34.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152799,154801}Shall I prepare you some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:36.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154801,156636}Yes, I'll be glad to drink some.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:39.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156636,159013}– With a lot of milk, as usual.\N– Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:43.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159931,163309}I'd like to ask him\Nwhat kind of food a beetle eats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163309,164769}But how do I get to the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:47.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:165395,167772}I can't count on Heinz's horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:49.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167772,169273}It can't go that far yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:52.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170817,172652}That leaves only…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172652,174112}A car, it appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:54.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174112,174862}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174862,177031}Apricot jam?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:02.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177031,182328}Yes. I tried it in London, at Dennis' house,\Nand it was delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:03.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182328,183579}Hmm…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.57,0:03:07.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:183579,187458}We have apricot jam here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:09.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187458,189127}but this is the only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190712,192171}That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192171,193631}It was a different brand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:194257,196050}Thought as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.71,0:03:20.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196718,200638}If you could remember the brand,\NI could order it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.30,0:03:23.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201305,203558}I don't really remember\Nwhat was the brand,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203975,206602}but I could tell it from the label.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:27.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:206602,207937}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207937,209397}In addition…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.39,0:03:32.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209397,212150}If we order it from abroad,\Nit will take several weeks, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:36.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213025,216696}I would like my grandfather\Nto try it just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:42.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217613,222410}In that case, I'll go visit a grocery store\Nin the town and order it there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222410,224370}Really? That would be terrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224370,225747}Thank you, Leighton.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226622,228416}That was an easy request.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.41,0:03:49.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228416,229709}All right, let me go at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:53.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229709,233963}Oh, is there anything else you want?\NI will go and see if they have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:56.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233963,236257}Oh? Are you going alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:04:00.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237592,240887}Oh, it is a simple task,\NI can handle it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.63,0:04:05.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241637,245016}I thought I could go with Leighton.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245683,246851}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.85,0:04:10.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:246851,250480}I don't have to travel on a seat.\NThe important thing is to get to the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:40.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276672,280468}That way I can go anywhere I want\Nwithout anybody's permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:301781,303741}Dad. It's a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.74,0:05:05.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303741,305827}There is a car parked\Nin the front of our store.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:08.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305827,308329}Yes. They're from the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:09.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308329,309956}Good morning, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:12.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309956,312708}Name the goods you need\Nand I'll bring them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312708,314293}Today's a bit unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:18.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314293,318381}I'd like to see every brand\Nof apricot jams you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:19.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318381,319173}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341988,343406}You're Colin, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:46.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343406,346075}I could tell it's you from the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:55.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:353124,355042}Nope, I can't tell which one it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:58.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:355042,358629}I wish I had asked for more details.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:00.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358629,360339}Maybe we could call her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:360339,361424}You mean the mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:03.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361424,363301}I'll contact them\Nand get back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:04.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363301,364468}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366345,367179}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:09.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367722,369015}Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.01,0:06:10.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369015,370600}How could she get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:15.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374312,375438}A brown dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.43,0:06:18.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375438,378316}Yes. It's beautiful and cheerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:378316,380276}What was its name…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:21.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380276,381152}Let me recall…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:22.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381152,382153}Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:23.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:382153,383696}Right, right! Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.69,0:06:26.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383696,386032}So its name is Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386032,388117}What is the name of\Nthe owner of that dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388117,389076}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389785,392663}I see. I finally know his name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.66,0:06:34.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:392663,394332}Lassie and John.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:37.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394332,397418}Sorry, I… am going now…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:40.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397418,400212}Do you know which way\Nis John's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:42.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400212,402173}But I…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:43.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402757,403841}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:50.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407178,410598}If you go this way,\Nthe road is going to split.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410598,413267}Turn left, and continue straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:56.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413267,416145}There will be houses that belong\Nto the mine employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:59.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416145,419774}I saw them.\NThey continue endlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:00.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419774,420399}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:02.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420399,422276}Which number is his house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:05.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422276,425613}Oh? House number?\NIf I recall right… it's…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429992,432453}Really, the same houses\Nall the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:14.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432453,434580}Does John live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:20.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:436916,440753}She doesn't know his name nor address,\Nyet she goes to visit him? So weird…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:22.92,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441712,442922}What a strange girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:24.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443589,444632}All right…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:31.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448010,451889}Who are you?\NWhat do you want from John?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:38.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456018,458312}I'm sorry, did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:41.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:458312,461399}Ah… No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:45.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:464276,465861}– Is this the place?\N– Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.61,0:07:48.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466612,468322}I wonder if John's here…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468322,470408}If you're looking for John,\Nhe's in the backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.40,0:07:52.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:470408,472910}Oh? What a cute little lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:55.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:472910,475287}I had underestimated you, Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.28,0:07:56.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475287,476831}Huh? Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:00.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478874,480167}Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:03.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480543,483254}Oh? What a funny boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483254,485548}So who are you, my dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.93,0:08:20.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498936,500312}Your friend came.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:22.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500312,502189}– Who is it?\N– She's a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502189,503149}Sandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:25.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503149,505067}No, that's not her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505067,507611}She's a beauty\Nwith long blond hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507611,508529}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:29.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509030,509572}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:33.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509572,513075}Don't peep like that,\Nit's bad manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:36.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513075,516120}She's waiting for you\Non the couch in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:37.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:516120,517204}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:42.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:520124,522835}That's really her.\NHow did she know where I live?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522835,524086}Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:524086,526297}Watch out!\NYou're going to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530885,532803}Look at yourself…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:55.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:533387,535556}Now you've done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:58.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536974,538059}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.77,0:09:01.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540770,541771}I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.11,0:09:09.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548110,549779}Wait a moment!\NI'll change my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550279,551280}Hey, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555951,557036}What's up, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:24.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563000,564794}We meet again, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564794,566837}Your name is Lassie, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568339,570549}I don't know how you\Ngot to know each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:33.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570549,573594}but I'm afraid you'll have to put up\Nwith Lassie until John comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574220,576013}"Put up"? She's lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:44.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:580643,584188}How did that girl know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584188,585397}Something's off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586065,587566}She's a real mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:56.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:593989,596659}My heart is still beating fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:02.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597952,602540}If she's not in the mansion, that means\NI wasn't seeing things and it really was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:11.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609171,611132}Oh, you're that lad\Nfrom the grocery store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612049,614051}Have you seen\Na girl in blue clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615136,617179}She's about 11-12 years old,\Nand has long blond hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:20.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617179,620808}If you had seen her,\Ntell me where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622017,623769}Who… Who's that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626147,627606}Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:28.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627606,628732}I just asked you a question!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629233,630860}Why did he run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:32.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630860,632736}Maybe he knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:35.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634947,635823}That way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.78,0:10:40.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638784,640035}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:13.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670149,673152}Why is he chasing me?\NI haven't done anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:17.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674695,677198}Why is this lad\Nrunning away from me?
Comment: 0,0:11:22.32,0:11:22.32,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:682328,682328}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:27.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:684538,687249}I can't believe this is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:29.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687249,689543}What to do?\NIt doesn't come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.04,0:11:31.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690044,691170}I'm coming in, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:36.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692171,696133}No, that won't work.\NYou have to wash it with warm water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696133,697176}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:47.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705517,707144}Oh? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:50.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709021,710147}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:52.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710147,712858}I brought eggs and cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:55.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713442,715861}Hey, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:05.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723035,725788}So it's you who shouldn't\Nbe underestimated, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:06.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:725788,726747}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:10.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726747,730668}Where did you meet her?\NWhat's her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:13.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730668,733545}Well… How to put it…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734171,735714}What does that matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:16.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735714,736548}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:32.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:751230,752273}I see, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:34.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752273,754483}I knew that it was his doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:36.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754483,756777}John is still acting like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:39.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756777,759989}Oh, right, I just remembered,\Nwhen we went to the waterway…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759989,761407}Thank you, Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:42.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761407,762408}Good morning, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:45.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:762408,765828}I see, so you're Sandy's friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765828,767079}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:49.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:767079,769123}We just got to know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.74,0:12:50.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:769748,770958}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:51.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770958,771792}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:59.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777589,779883}Yes, let's do it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:01.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:779883,781593}He'll be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:02.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781593,782636}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:04.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782636,784305}Oh, you're finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:784596,786265}Good morning, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786265,788225}Colin told me where you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:09.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:788225,789977}I, I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789977,791562}Well, what to say…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:15.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791812,795065}When you saw me falling…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.52,0:13:16.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795524,796775}Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:18.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796775,798027}Hey, Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:19.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798027,799903}Wait, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:20.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799903,800988}You stink. You stink!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:22.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800988,802990}You reek of paint, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:802990,804158}I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:26.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804158,806285}Tell me I'm right, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.28,0:13:31.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806285,811749}I had thought we could prepare a cake today,\Nso I had asked Sandy to bring eggs and cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:32.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811749,812624}A cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:35.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812624,815210}Perfect timing.\NWe have a guest, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815210,816003}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816003,817755}It's not going to be so easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.75,0:13:39.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817755,819465}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.46,0:13:41.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819465,821508}– You can thank yourself for it.\N– That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:47.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:822259,827014}John, because of the paint, your clothes\Nmust be washed immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.97,0:13:51.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827973,831018}I can wash them, so long\Nas you make the cake, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:54.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831518,834021}Oh, don't worry, I'm going\Nto have someone else make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:55.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834313,835731}Am I right, Sandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.73,0:13:57.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835731,837441}That's right, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839443,840527}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:03.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841070,843530}Sandy told us that she\Nis going to make the cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.07,0:14:06.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844073,846533}Oh, Priscilla,\Nyou're going to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:08.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847493,848494}Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849328,852831}I haven't made cakes before…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:15.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852831,855250}It'll be fine, I'll teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:19.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855918,859463}Sandy's good at making\Nwhat she likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:20.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:859463,860381}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:21.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860381,861965}You know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:26.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862841,866553}Is your owner always like that?\NIt is very amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:28.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866929,868472}All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.47,0:14:32.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868472,872643}I'll wash your clothes, son,\Nand I'll look forward to the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:33.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872643,873352}What about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:35.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873352,875312}You'll help the girls out, naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.31,0:14:36.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875312,876855}It'll be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:878774,880567}All right. Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891245,893789}All right, John, you'll\Nlight up the fireplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:54.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893789,894623}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.62,0:14:57.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894623,897209}– Priscilla, you can crack the eggs.\N– Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:918313,919273}Priscilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:19.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919273,919898}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.89,0:15:22.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919898,922776}You need to separate\Nthe yolk from the white.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:23.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922776,923944}How to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.36,0:15:25.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924361,925320}Here, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:27.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925946,927322}You do it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:33.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931034,933829}Wow, you're so skilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:36.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935330,936832}What do we do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:37.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936832,937624}Hand it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.58,0:15:41.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940586,941837}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:43.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942463,943755}Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.67,0:15:52.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950679,952723}– Now let's add some water and milk.\N– Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:956477,957603}All right, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:06.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965319,966236}Wanna try?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:06.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966236,966987}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:10.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968447,970491}The fireplace is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:14.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972784,974369}Good. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.36,0:16:15.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:974369,975996}Sorry, what do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975996,978290}Oh, no, don't move\Nyour hand like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:20.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978290,980334}Here, I'll show you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:22.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980334,982878}Thanks, ma'am.\NHow do I mix it correctly?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.33,0:16:26.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983337,986089}You mix it like this\Nuntil it forms kind of horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986089,988467}Horns… Like cow horns?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:31.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:988467,991261}Look, here are the horns, Priscilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991261,992304}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.39,0:16:47.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004399,1007361}So her name is Priscilla…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.37,0:17:00.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017371,1020207}All right, all that's left\Nis to wait until it's baked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:01.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020207,1021124}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:09.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026838,1029633}Making cakes is so fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:11.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030551,1031969}Have you finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:12.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031969,1032636}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.51,0:17:15.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033512,1035097}Oh, I just remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:21.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038976,1041395}What food should I feed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:24.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042229,1044022}Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:26.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044022,1046984}Put a piece of cotton inside,\Nsoaked with water and sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1046984,1048569}Water and sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:32.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048569,1052281}Yes. But to be honest, I don't think\Nit's very happy in such a cramped place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052281,1053615}Y-You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:36.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053615,1056785}Tell me, what kind of place\Nwould be good, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:37.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056785,1057744}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:40.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057744,1060581}First, get a larger box\Nand put some soil inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:43.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060581,1063417}I think it would be good\Nif it had some plant. Also…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:54.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072926,1074595}He stopped running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:56.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1074595,1076471}I can't run anymore…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:59.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077889,1079308}Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:07.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086398,1087566}How does it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:08.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087566,1088650}Just perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097326,1098243}I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:18.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098243,1098994}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:20.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098994,1100287}What is this smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.28,0:18:22.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100287,1102748}– Welcome back!\N– Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:27.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104082,1107419}It's so nice to come back\Nand find such a fine smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:28.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107419,1108879}Oh, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:30.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1108879,1110756}A chiffon cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.34,0:18:32.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111340,1112883}Looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112883,1114259}Did Mom make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.55,0:18:35.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1114551,1115761}No, not this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:38.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1115761,1118764}These two girls did everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:42.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119556,1122225}– Good evening, sir.\N– Good evening, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122225,1123477}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:46.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123769,1126355}Sam, about the thing\Nwe had talked about…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:46.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126355,1126980}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:50.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127648,1130484}What is this good smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.44,0:18:53.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131443,1133445}It's a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:54.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133445,1134655}I'll help myself to a slice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:00.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138241,1140118}Who is this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:01.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140452,1141953}You won't like it, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:06.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141953,1146124}The owner said he'll visit us again\Nwith his granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:07.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146541,1147751}What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.75,0:19:11.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147751,1151380}This is not a good place\Nfor children.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:13.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151380,1153715}I'm so stressed\Nabout this entire affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:16.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153715,1156843}I got so hungry\Nyou wouldn't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:18.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157094,1158512}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:20.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1159262,1160722}Now even Colin's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.72,0:19:22.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160722,1162099}Truly a flood of guests today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162099,1163141}Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:27.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164142,1167521}John, I got caught\Nby some strange man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:28.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167521,1168730}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:30.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1168730,1170565}Who are you calling a strange man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1170565,1172526}It's your fault\Nfor jumping to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:35.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173568,1175529}Leighton?\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:38.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175779,1178115}How can you ask\Nme that question, miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:39.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178115,1179991}Please be a little more responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:42.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179991,1182077}Why did you hide in my car?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:46.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182077,1186832}What would happen if you were\Nabducted or something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.83,0:19:47.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186832,1187958}I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:51.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1190377,1191336}All right, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:54.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192754,1194214}You have to go already?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:20:01.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1196883,1201012}I came here without anybody's\Npermission. It was selfish of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.01,0:20:02.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1201012,1202723}I caused trouble to Leighton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:07.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1203724,1207227}You don't look like a bad girl\Nto me, Priscilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:09.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1208562,1209730}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1211022,1212232}Thank you, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1212232,1213316}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:15.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214317,1215819}Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:19.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1215819,1219823}Because we met,\NI got to meet many nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219823,1221241}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:25.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222117,1225829}Thank you for telling me\Nhow to make cakes, Sandy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:27.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225829,1227247}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.91,0:20:28.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227914,1228999}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:33.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1228999,1233003}I will take good care of your gift,\Njust like you taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1233003,1234171}My gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:36.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234171,1236298}The little jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.25,0:20:40.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238258,1240010}Thank you, too, Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:40.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240010,1240802}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:43.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240802,1243472}– Let's go.\N– Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:48.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1248101,1248977}Priscilla…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:54.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251730,1254733}I apologize for\Nwhat happened today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.23,0:20:59.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258236,1259905}Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:00.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259905,1260655}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:06.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265368,1266828}Priscilla…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:09.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266828,1269039}She left without trying\Neven a single slice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:10.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1269039,1270081}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:11.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270081,1271416}Wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271416,1273794}Where did I hear that name again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1273794,1275754}Priscilla… Priscilla…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:18.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276588,1278882}Ah! I just remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:19.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1278882,1279966}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:22.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1279966,1282052}How do I explain this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.05,0:21:25.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282052,1285764}Priscilla is the name of\NMr. Radling's granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:29.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287432,1289100}So that girl was…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:33.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289100,1293647}Come to think of it, that man\Ncame by the car from the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:40.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1295232,1300111}I… I said too much in front of her…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.11,0:21:42.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300111,1302030}Isn't that lovely, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:44.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302030,1304199}Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.19,0:21:46.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304199,1306952}Now that we know\Nwhere Priscilla lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:49.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306952,1309120}we can deliver the cake to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:50.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309120,1310330}Good idea!
Comment: 0,0:21:58.38,0:21:58.38,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1318380,1318380}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.84,0:22:04.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1320841,1324177}{\i1}Priscilla is going back\Nto Scotland tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.17,0:22:06.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324177,1326304}{\i1}We just made friends with her…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.30,0:22:09.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326304,1329224}{\i1}I have an idea.\NLet's all go to the Rocky Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:12.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329224,1332435}{\i1}It's where the sunset\Ncan be seen the longest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:15.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332435,1335438}{\i1}Next episode:\N"Priscilla's Last Disobedience".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:16.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1335438,1336898}{\i1}Be sure to watch!
